photographed at an automatic teller machine using a bank card
belonging to one of the rape victims, police said.
   Authorities said the rapes took place between 1983 and last
November. Most of the victims were women in their 20s who were alone
at home, police said.
   The assailant often took the victim's bank card and forced her to
reveal the personal identification code necessary to withdraw money,
police said.
